    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014always garage-kept and treated with so much love. You really won't find a scratch on it. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be absolutely thrilled with it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
